OL,6,GAs of 9am BST on Monday morning, the
OL,7,GBBC News Channel in the UK was
OL,8,Gformally merged with its
OL,9,Ginternational sister channel, BBC
OL,10,GWorld News.
OL,12,FThe result is a single TV news
OL,13,Fchannel with an international focus
OL,14,Fbut with an ability to "opt out" of
OL,15,Fthe main international version of the
OL,16,Fchannel, to allow the UK audience to
OL,17,Freceive dedicated reporting and
OL,18,Fanalysis of particularly significant
OL,19,Fdomestic stories.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G1/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
