PN,35402
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1683718932
OL,6,FViewers in the UK also get a
OL,7,Fsimulcast of BBC Breakfast, the main
OL,8,FBBC One news programmes (weekdays)
OL,9,Fand BBC Two's Newsnight. And later
OL,10,Fthis month, Nicky Campbell's Radio 5
OL,11,FLive programme will also appear on
OL,12,Fthe UK version of the TV news channel.
OL,14,FWhilst the simulcasting is reducing
OL,15,Fthe programme options available in
OL,16,Fthe UK, there is the counter argument
OL,17,Fthat it is potentially bringing
OL,18,Fexisting programming to an additional
OL,19,Faudience.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G2/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
