PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F354A1683718932
OL,6,FSome would say the BBC is cynically
OL,7,Fusing the BBC One/Two/Radio 5
OL,8,Fsimulcasting as a means of increasing
OL,9,Fthe amount of UK-specific content
OL,10,Fshown on the news channel, in an
OL,11,Fattempt to placate Ofcom.
OL,13,FIt's very early days but how is the
OL,14,Fnew channel shaping up so far?
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G3/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
