OL,6,FWhilst there are definitely rough
OL,7,Fedges, it does not feel anywhere
OL,8,Fclose to being as unappealing for a
OL,9,FUK audience as many predicted. And
OL,10,Flet's face it, we've had simulcast
OL,11,Fprogramming on BBC News Channel/BBC
OL,12,FWorld News for quite a while now ` it
OL,13,Fall feels quite familiar at this
OL,14,Fstage.
OL,16,FUltimately, even an international
OL,17,Fchannel from BBC News is going to
OL,18,Fhave a UK slant.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G4/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
