OL,6,FThat said, for some time now, it has
OL,7,Ffelt like international viewers are
OL,8,Fbeing subjected to more UK-specific
OL,9,Fcontent as a result of the
OL,10,Fsimulcasting across the two news
OL,11,Fchannels.
OL,13,FBut how might we get a better balance
OL,14,Ffor the two audiences (UK v
OL,15,FInternational) whilst continuing to
OL,16,Flive within the current budget
OL,17,Fconstraints?
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G5/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
