OL,6,FBBC News believes a bigger portion of
OL,7,Fits resourcing should now be invested
OL,8,Fin digital production ` primarily the
OL,9,Fwebsite operation and associated
OL,10,Fsocial media channels.
OL,12,FUK audiences still have a rich pool
OL,13,Fof domestic coverage online and via
OL,14,FBBC One news programming. And these
OL,15,Fsources are, undeniably, where the
OL,16,Fvast majority of the BBC audience in
OL,17,Fthe UK get their news.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G6/19
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
