OL,6,FFor example, a split screen
OL,7,Farrangement, with the international
OL,8,Fcontent playing out uninterrupted,
OL,9,Falongside a text-based UK service.
OL,10,FLower-third real estate could
OL,11,Fdefinitely be put to much better use
OL,12,Ftoo.
OL,14,FThe UK opt-out that we saw on Monday
OL,15,Fran from 2.20pm until shortly before
OL,16,F5pm and concentrated on a single
OL,17,Fstory ` the sentencing of Olivia
OL,18,FPratt-Korbel's killer.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
