OL,6,FWhilst UK viewers would want to see
OL,7,Fimportant domestic stories reported
OL,8,Fproperly, there's a happy medium to
OL,9,Fbe had here ` and over two-and-a-half
OL,10,Fhours of almost continuous coverage
OL,11,Fof a single story, with a lot of
OL,12,Frepetition, doesn't feel like it's
OL,13,Fhitting the mark.
OL,15,FOn Monday afternoon, UK viewers
OL,16,Fdidn't get an international news
OL,17,Fservice nor did they get proper
OL,18,Fcoverage of UK domestic stories.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
