OL,6,FBut, the lead-up to the interview,
OL,7,Fthe interview itself and the analysis
OL,8,Fthat followed ran from 10.44am until
OL,9,F12.15pm ` and no other stories were
OL,10,Fcovered during that time.  Providing
OL,11,Ftext-based coverage of other stories
OL,12,Fand/or an ability for viewers to
OL,13,Fswitch back to the international
OL,14,Fstream would be worth considering.
OL,16,FOverall, not brilliant but not awful.
OL,17,F With more thought and structure,
OL,18,Fthere's a workable solution in there
OL,19,Fsomewhere.
