OL,6,FClean Feed understands there was a
OL,7,Fplan to completely change the BBC
OL,8,FNews branding.  Lambie-Nairn's iconic
OL,9,Fglobe device has been in use since
OL,10,FApril 2008 and some elements of the
OL,11,Fbranding stretch as far back as 1999.
OL,13,FCost and timeframes caused the
OL,14,Fbranding replacement plans to be put
OL,15,Fon hold.
OL,17,FThere was though a desire to get the
OL,18,Fhigh-profile News division properly
OL,19,Fon board with the BBC Chameleon
OL,20,Fbranding (the branding templates/
OL,21,Felements associated with the rollout
OL,22,Fof the new BBC masterbrand logo).
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
