OL,6,FIn 2022, the new BBC blocks were
OL,7,Fintroduced to News branding (e.g.,
OL,8,Ftitle sequences) in a form referred
OL,9,Fto internally as "Chameleon Lite".
OL,10,FThe Gill Sans BBC blocks were simply
OL,11,Freplaced with the new "Reithed" BBC
OL,12,Flogo.
OL,14,FFull implementation of the Chameleon
OL,15,Fbranding was deferred because a more
OL,16,Fcomprehensive update of News branding
OL,17,Fwas planned.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
OL,4,Cbecome one
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}       G14/19
