OL,6,FBut with those plans for a full
OL,7,Frefresh of News branding later put on
OL,8,Fice, an alternative, short-term
OL,9,Fsolution would be required.  There
OL,10,Fwas still a desire to implement
OL,11,Fproper Chameleon branding.
OL,13,FIn recent weeks, the BBC began
OL,14,Fsuggesting that 3rd April was merely
OL,15,Fthe start of a journey and should not
OL,16,Fbe regarded as a "big bang" change of
OL,17,Fapproach for the rolling news service.
OL,3,CBBC News Channel and BBC World News
