OL,6,FSomewhat surprising given they've
OL,7,Fbeen planning these changes since at
OL,8,Fleast last summer. But then, the BBC
OL,9,Fhas never been known for moving at
OL,10,Fgreat pace.
OL,12,FHowever, the recent comments about a
OL,13,F"soft launch" gave some hope that
OL,14,Fthere'd be no rushed decisions about
OL,15,Fon-screen branding.
OL,17,FUnfortunately, they chose to press
OL,18,Fahead with an ill-considered
OL,19,FChameleon update.
