OL,6,FThe familiar BBC News title sequence
OL,7,F(on the news channel and BBC One) has
OL,8,Fbeen updated with the Chameleon
OL,9,Fbranding (BBC blocks at the top,
OL,10,F'NEWS' branding at the bottom).  The
OL,11,Fglobe device has been shunted to the
OL,12,Fright slightly, to avoid direct
OL,13,Fcontact with the BBC blocks.
OL,15,FThe result: horrible.
OL,17,FAnd many news programmes continue to
OL,18,Fuse the version of the titles
OL,19,Ffeaturing the 2022 patch logo.
OL,20,F There's also a mishmash of branding
OL,21,Fon trails.
