OL,6,FAnd on stings, the 'NEWS' logo at the
OL,7,Fbottom of the screen more often than
OL,8,Fnot has the lower-third graphic
OL,9,Foverlaid.
OL,11,FHowever, Clean Feed understands that
OL,12,Fa recreation of the Lambie-Nairn
OL,13,Fgraphics is coming soon. So expect
OL,14,Fthe title sequences to better
OL,15,Faccommodate the Chameleon branding.
OL,17,FBut will the updated globe device be
OL,18,Fa worthy rival to the wizardry of the
OL,19,FLambie-Nairn agency? We shall see.
